app: Automatically save/sync/upload my new Google contacts to a Google Drive spreadsheet #graajkumaar
description:
Automatically save/sync/upload my new Google contacts to a Google Drive spreadsheet #graajkumaar Trigger service: GOOGLE CONTACTS
New contact added: This Trigger fires every time a new Google Contact is created.

Action service: GOOGLE DRIVE
Add row to spreadsheet: This Action will add a single row to the bottom of the first worksheet of the spreadsheet you specify. NOTE: A new spreadsheet is created after 2000 rows.

If new contact added, then add row to spreadsheet in Microsoft@Hotmail.com’s Google Drive.
